description: ErrorControlSystem is a .NET library created to automate handling .NET Windows-Base application exceptions and raise that to a sql server. This exception handler have some features as screen capturing, fetch server date time in exception occurrence time and etc.
summary: This is a C#.Net project's for manage Exceptions of your .Net applications by handling and logging that. This is a .dll modules to provide error handling worker on your app background's.
title: Error Control System
